.*  Keyword:  MBR
.********************************************
:HELP NAME='RUNCLSTM/USESRCMBR'.
Source member (USESRCMBR) - Help
:XH3.Source member (USESRCMBR)
:P.
Specifies the name of the source file member that contains
the SQL statements to be run.

:IMHELP name='COM/REQPARM'.

:EHELP.

