.********************************************
:HELP NAME='RUNCLSTM/NAMING'.
Naming convention (NAMING) - Help
:XH3.Naming convention (NAMING)
:P.
Select whether the SQL naming convention or the system
naming convention is to be used.
:IMHELP name='COM/OPTPARM'.
:P.
:IMHELP name='COM/VALUES'.

:PARML.
:PT.:PK DEF.*SYS:EPK.
:PD.The system naming convention will be used.
:PT.:PV.*SQL:EPV.
:PD.The SQL naming convention will be used.
:EPARML.

